text: Zeds Dead is an electronic music group from Toronto, Canada. They released original music and remixes from 2009 to 2010 before becoming a name on the international touring circuit. The group has two members, Dylan Mamid aka DC and Zachary Rapp-Rovan aka Hooks. They explore different genres that combine aspects of dubstep, UK garage, house, electro house, hip-hop, glitch, drum and bass, and more. == References == *elektrodaily interview with Zeds Dead *Dallas Observer article on Zeds Dead Category:Electronic music
